<html xmlns='http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml'>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=utf-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <meta content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1' name='viewport' />
    <title>Invited</title>
    <link rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.googleapis.com' />
    <link rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.gstatic.com' crossorigin />
    <link
      href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@700&display=swap'
      rel='stylesheet'
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <table style='margin: 2rem auto;'>
      <tbody>
        <tr style='text-align: center;'>
          <td>
            <h1
              style='text-align: center; font-family: "Tajawal", sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 60px; line-height: 120%; text-align: center; margin: 0;
letter-spacing: -0.05em; color: #2A3037;'
            >
              مبروك ، لقد تم دعوتك الى ردزام!
            </h1>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <p
              style='font-family: "Tajawal", sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 180%; text-align: center; color: #000000; opacity: 0.8;'
            >
              هذا هو رمز الدعوة الخاص بك:
            </p>
            <h3
              style='text-align: center; font-family: "Tajawal", sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 48px; line-height: 120%; text-align: center; margin: 0;
letter-spacing: -0.05em; color: #2A3037;'
            >
              {{invitationCode}}
            </h3>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <p
              style='font-family: "Tajawal", sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 180%; text-align: center; color: #000000; opacity: 0.8;'
            >
              يرجى ادخال الرمز الى الرابط التالي لتكن جزءًا من ردزام:
              <a href='{{origin}}/invite'>مرحبًا بك في ردزام</a>
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <br />
          <br />
        </tr>
        <tr style='text-align: center;'>
          <span
            style='font-family: "Tajawal", sans-serif; font-size: 8px; line-height: 180%; text-align: center; color: #000000; opacity: 0.7;'
          >
            {{randomText}}
          </span>
          <span
            style='font-family: "Tajawal", sans-serif; font-size: 8px; line-height: 180%; text-align: center; color: #000000; opacity: 0.7;'
          >
            •
          </span>
          <a
            href='https://redxam.ae'
            style='font-family: "Tajawal", sans-serif; font-size: 8px; line-height: 180%; text-align: center; color: #000000; opacity: 0.7;'
          >
            redxam.ae
          </a>
        </tr>
        <tr style='text-align: center;'>
          <a href='https://bit.ly/3sDVHhe'><img src='cid:linkedin@ico' /></a>
          <a href='https://bit.ly/33oAfEe'><img src='cid:twitter@ico' /></a>
          <a href='https://bit.ly/3uUt3el'><img src='cid:facebook@ico' /></a>
          <a href='https://bit.ly/33qB53x'><img src='cid:telegram@ico' /></a>
          <a href='https://bit.ly/3HVyJZe'><img src='cid:discord@ico' /></a>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

  </body>
</html>